Since the beginning of the coronavirus pandemic, theories have swirled online about its source.
But they present new information about the potential source of the pandemic, so we wanted to review publicly available evidence about the source and spread of the coronavirus — and what is still unproven.
Coronavirus came from batsScientists widely believe that bats are the source of the novel coronavirus.
